description: IAR Systems Group AB engages in the provision of software for programming of processors in embedded systems. The company is headquartered in Uppsala, Uppsala and currently employs 212 full-time employees.  Its activities comprise one business segment: IAR Systems. The firm specializes in the development of tools for embedded systems. Its software solutions are implemented to products based on 8-, 16-, and 32-bit microcontrollers, which are used in a range of areas, such as industrial automation, medical devices, consumer electronics, telecommunication and automotive products. Furthermore, its partners network comprises Freescale Semiconductor, Fujitsu, Texas Instruments, Samsung, NXP Semiconductors, Toshiba, Seiko Epson Corporation, and Infineon Technologies, among others. The firm operates through a number of subsidiaries located in the United States, England, Norway, China, Japan, and Finland, among others.
naics: Computer Systems Design and Related Services
